Uses of Package
gruppe.irc

  • Packages that use gruppe.irc 
    Package Description
    gruppe.irc
    This package contains the IRCConnection class itself and the MessageEvent class that is used to pass information about events from the IRCConnection class to the attached listener objects.
    gruppe.irc.messageListeners
    This package contains the MessageListener interface that needs to be implemented by any listeners that is to be connected to the IRCConnection object.
